ernmarylandchronicle.com/2018/03/26/smcso-releases-timeline-of-great-mills-high-school-shooting/|title=SMCSO releases timeline of Great Mills High School shooting |date=March 26, 2018 |work=TheSouthernMarylanChronicle}}</ref> \n|-\n|{{Dts|March 21, 2018}}\n|[[Shadrinsk]], Russia\n| Student, 13\n|\n| 7 injured\n| A 13-year-old girl opened fire with a gas pistol at her school in Russia's Kurgan region, injuring seven seventh graders. The victims suffered bruises and scrapes.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rferl.org/a/russia-kurgan-school-shooting/29112975.html|title=Russian Schoolgirl Shoots Classmates With Gas Pistol, Seven Injured |date=March 21, 2018 |work=RadioFreeEurope/RadioLiberty}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|April 18, 2018}}\n|[[Sterlitamak]], Russia\n| Student\n|\n| 4 injured\n| Four people were hospitalized after a knife-wielding teenage student attacked his school in Russia's Bashkortostan region, in the city of Sterlitamak. The attacker wounded three girls and a teacher, and set a classroom on fire.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rferl.org/a/three-students-teacher-hospitalized-after-teen-attacks-school-in-russia/29174568.html|title=Three Students, Teacher Hospitalized After Teen Attacks School In Russia |date=April 18, 2018 |work=RadioFreeEurope/RadioLiberty}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|April 20, 2018}}\n|[[Ocala, Florida]], United States\n| Sky Bouche, 19\n|\n| 1 injured\n| A former Forest High School student entered the school with a guitar case containing a 1930 sawed-off shotgun. He retrieved the gun in the washroom, and entered the hallway. Bouche was ready to fire and reportedly had seen multiple students, but had a strike of morality before firing. He later stated when the moment came, and he saw a female students distress in reaction to seeing him, he couldn't bring himself to hurt anyone. Instead he fired a shot at a nearby closed door, without aiming. He later claimed that he \"didn't think the gun would fire\". A 17-year-old male student in the classroom was wounded after he was shot in the ankle. Bouche then entered the classroom of one of his former teachers, and surrendered peacefully to the responding SRO. <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ocala.com/news/20190420/one-year-after-shooting-at-ocalas-forest-high-school|title=One year after the shooting at Ocala\u2019s Forest High School |date=April 20, 2019 |work=OcalaStarBanner}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|April 27, 2018}}\n| [[Mizhi county]], [[Yulin]], [[Shaanxi]], China\n| Zhao Zewei, 28\n| 9 dead\n| 10 injured\n| Nine students were stabbed to death and 10 injured in a knife attack outside a school in northern China. The man who carried out the attack was reportedly a former student, taking revenge for having been bullied at the school. The dead were seven girls and two boys aged 12 to 15.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-43921567|title=China stabbings: Nine students killed in Shaanxi |date=April 28, 2018 |work=BBC News}}</ref>\n|-\n|May 25, 2018\n|[[Palmdale, California]], US\n| Student, 14\n| \n|1 injured\n|A 14 year old male opened fire with a rifle at roughly 7:00&nbsp;a.m. at [[Highland High School (Palmdale, California)|Highland High School]] campus and then walked into a bathroom. The shots wounded one former schoolmate, a male who was shot in his arm. The suspect shot 10 rounds. He then dumped the gun in a field before he was taken into custody in a nearby shopping center.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.dailynews.com/2018/05/11/deputies-respond-to-report-of-man-with-a-gun-at-palmdales-highland-high-school//|title= Student shot at Highland High School in Palmdale, former schoolmate in custody |last=|first=|date=2018-05-18|work=CBS Interactive Inc.|access-date=2018-05-19|language=en-US}}</ref>\n|-\n|May 18, 2018\n|[[Santa Fe, Texas]], US\n|Dimitrios Pagourtzis, 17\n|10 dead\n|14 injured\n|[[Santa Fe High School shooting]]. A student armed with a shotgun and a .38 revolver smuggled under his coat opened fire on [[Santa Fe High School (Texas)|Santa Fe High School]] campus, killing 10 people and wounding 13 more, as well as injuring himself.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/05/18/us/school-shooting-santa-fe-texas.html|title=Texas School Shooting: 10 Dead, 10 Hurt, and Many Not Surprised It Happened|last=Fernandez|first=Manny|date=2018-05-18|work=The New York Times|access-date=2018-05-19|last2=Fausset|first2=Richard|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331|last3=Bidgood|first3=Jess}}</ref>\n|-\n|May 25, 2018\n|[[Noblesville, Indiana]], US\n| Student, 13\n| \n|2 injured\n|[[Noblesville West Middle School shooting]]. A student opened fire at 9:06.<ref name=\"f59-what-we-know\">{{cite news|title=Here\u2019s what we know about the Noblesville West Middle School shooting that injured student, teacher|url=http://fox59.com/2018/05/25/heres-what-we-know-about-the-noblesville-west-middle-school-shooting/|accessdate=25 May 2018|agency=FOX59}}</ref> a.m. on [[Noblesville West Middle School]] campus, injuring two; an adult and a teenager. After the incident, the suspect came into custody.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.cbsnews.com/news/indiana-school-shooting-report-of-shots-fired-at-noblesville-west-middle-school/|title=Police: 2 injured in shooting at Noblesville West Middle School in Indiana|last=|first=|date=2018-05-18|work=CBS Interactive Inc.|access-date=2018-05-19|language=en-US}}</ref>\n|-\n|October 17, 2018\n|[[Kerch]]\n| Vladislav Roslyakov, 18\n|21 dead\n|70 injured\n|The [[Kerch Polytechnic College massacre]]. An 18-year-old student at the [[Kerch Polytechnic College]] set off explosives in the school and began shooting, killing 20. The shooter was highly inspired by the [[Columbine High School Massacre]], even going as far as wearing the same clothes as one of the two shooters involved in that attack.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-45891201|title=Gun attack at Crimea college kills 19|date=October 17, 2018|via=www.bbc.com}}</ref>\n|-\n|December 17, 2018\n|[[Haridwar, Uttarakhand]