ingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/10/10/AR2007101001486.html|work=[[The Washington Post]]|accessdate = 2009-03-07}}</ref>\n|-\n| October 11, 2007\n| [[Amsterdam]], Netherlands\n| H\u00fcseyin P., 14\n| 1 dead\n|\n| A 14-year-old student, identified only as H\u00fcseyin P., stabbed 16-year-old classmate Youssef Mokhtari to death at a school in the [[Slotervaart (former borough)|Slotervaart]] borough of [[Amsterdam]]. The victim had reportedly made a joke about the surname of the perpetrator.<ref name=\"adnl12loct\">{{cite news|first=Tonny|last=van der Mee|author2=Robin Rotman  |title=Dader steekpartij dreigde eerder|date=2007-10-12|work=[[Algemeen Dagblad]]|url =http://www.ad.nl/amsterdam/stad/article1737946.ece|accessdate = 2009-04-18|language = Dutch}}</ref>\n|-\n| November 7, 2007\n| [[Tuusula]], Finland\n| Pekka-Eric Auvinen, 18\n| 9 dead\n| 1 injured\n| [[Jokela school shooting]]. 18-year-old student Pekka-Eric Auvinen opened fire with a [[.22 Long Rifle|.22-caliber]] [[semi-automatic handgun|semi-automatic]] [[SIG Mosquito|SIG Mosquito pistol]] at [[Jokela High School]], in [[Tuusula]], Finland. Six students, the school principal, and the school nurse were killed. The forty-minute attack ended when Auvinen shot himself in the head, later dying that evening at a [[Helsinki]] hospital.\n|-\n| December 11, 2007\n| [[Gurgaon]],<br>[[Haryana]],<br>India\n| Akash Vadav, 14;<br>Vikas Yadav, 13\n| 1 dead\n|\n| 14-year-old student Abhishek Tyagi was shot five times at the Euro International School, in [[Gurgaon]], India. Two other students, 14-year-old Akash Vadav and 13-year-old Vikas Yadav, were charged in connection with the shooting.<ref name=\"hindustani1212\">{{cite news|title=School students shoot classmate for \u2018bullying\u2019|date=2007-12-12|url =http://hindustantimes.com/StoryPage/StoryPage.aspx?id=df416321-98a6-4572-b0bf-c6c5fbf29902&MatchID1=4604&TeamID1=6&TeamID2=7&MatchType1=1&SeriesID1=1157&MatchID2=4575&TeamID3=8&TeamID4=2&MatchType2=1&Serie